              <h3>Mission</h3>
              <p>To empower individuals of all ages and abilities by providing high-quality karate training that promotes physical and mental wellness. We aim to build confidence, discipline, and self-defense skills in children and pregnant women, creating a supportive and inclusive environment for everyone to grow.</p>
              <h3>Vision</h3>
              <p>To be a leading academy that promotes health, fitness, and personal growth through karate. We envision a community where every participant, regardless of age or background, has the opportunity to develop strength, resilience, and self-assurance.</p>
